rows.label: qst102104_msg0004
rows.name: How do you like the merc life?

rows.label: qst102104_msg0101
rows.name:
Me defeat my three enemies
and come here, quick-quick.

rows.label: qst102104_msg0103
rows.name:
Everyone late. Mercenary work
is group activity, so me wish
others would get with program.

rows.label: qst102104_msg0202
rows.name:
Me not quite grasp yet who is where,
what is what in village.

rows.label: qst102104_msg0203
rows.name:
Nopon legs stubby, moving around
is pain, and so life miserable for now.
